{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_02",
  "title": "愛歌う星の継承者 2話 聴けば聴くほど",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん、レッスンの後のご飯は美味しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ the food after lessons is delicious‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "分からないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "何が分からないんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What don't you understand?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回の企画、どうして琴乃やさくらじゃなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why was Suzu chosen instead of",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "すずが選ばれたのか、よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotonoor Sakura for this project?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "普通に考えるなら、妹の琴乃なり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Logically‚ it should be Kotono‚ Mana's sister‚ or Sakura‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈と縁の深いさくらが選ばれるのが妥当でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "who has a deep connection with Mana‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "その方が、テレビ的には話題性があるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That way‚ there would be more buzz and attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "芽衣はすずにゃんが猫っぽくて可愛いからかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's because Suzu-nyan is cute and cat-like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "って思ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そ、そう思うのは芽衣だけですわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's only Mei's opinion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私が星見プロで一番歌がうまいからに決まっています！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was chosen because I'm the best singer at Hoshimi Pro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずはまだまだこれからでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu still has a long way to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "今この時点での歌唱力だけなら、もっと上はいるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's singing‚ there is better choice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.71,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "り、莉央さん？　すずだって、歌は上手で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rio-san? Suzu is actually a skilled singer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに！　芽衣、瑠依ちゃんの歌聴きたいかも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Exactly! Mei wants to hear Rui-chan's singing too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、ちょっと芽衣まで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait‚ even Mei thinks so?…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "あああなた達！　私に喧嘩を売っているんですわね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Y-Y-Y-Y-You guys! Are you picking a fight with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そこまでおっしゃるのなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're saying that‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "今回の仕事を立派にやり遂げて、証明してみせますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "then I'll prove it by doing this job perfectly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私が、一番、麻奈様の曲を歌いこなせるということを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll show that I'm the one who can master Mana-sama's songs the best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "次の伝説は、私、成宮すずがつくるということを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next legend will be created by me‚ Suzu Narumiya!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2766666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "随分と大きく出たわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's quite ambitious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "口だけにならないといいけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope she's not just all talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "成宮家の人間たるもの、言った言葉に責任は持ちますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a member of the Narumiya family‚ I take responsibility for my words.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "今から特訓します！　芽衣、付き合って下さいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll start training from now on! Mei‚ please support me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいよ～、これ食べ終わったら――って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ after I finish eating…wait",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はまだ食べてるよーっ！　引っ張らないで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei is still eating‚ don't pull me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、これであの子のステージが楽しみになったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ I'm looking forward to her stage now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　莉央さん、それはどういう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? R-Rio-san‚ what do you mean…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの子は暴走するくらい張り切った方が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl performs better when she's driven to the edge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "実力以上のパフォーマンスを出すものね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She'll deliver a performance that exceeds her abilities…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もしかして、わざとですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you doing it on purpose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "すずのこと、よく見てるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're observing Suzu closely‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かりやすい子だもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's an easy-to-read girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
